Package: NanoSeqTools
Title: This function loads all the files one would need for the analysis of Nanoseq data.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Amoolya", "Srinivasa", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The input for this function would be the list of directories containing the NanoSeq results. The function gives a data structure as the output which has all the data frames for Mutation Burden analysis, Single base Substitutions and Indel Signature analysis in the results object as a list.
